### Replace with your actual Google OAuth2 ID token
@token = YOUR_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

### ── Add ──

### Add two positive numbers
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/add/3/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add with negative number
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/add/-3/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add floats
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/add/1.5/2.3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Subtract ──

### Subtract
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/subtract/10/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Subtract with negative result
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/subtract/3/10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Multiply ──

### Multiply
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/multiply/3/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Multiply by zero
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/multiply/5/0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Divide ──

### Divide
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/divide/10/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Divide by zero (expects 400)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/divide/5/0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Edge cases ──

### No authentication (expects 401)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/add/1/2

### Invalid token (expects 401)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/add/1/2
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token

### Invalid input: string (expects 422)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/add/abc/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
